{"tid":2035199,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京全國揀選黨員到香港負責指導教學工作","createTime":"2020-05-25T17:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T17:48:02.000Z","uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"912ecce999357f501a6062d89dadcbfa9d2f29eb","tid":2035199,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul0525a-05252020055046.html/BrainWash_mand.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2Fwul0525a-05252020055046.html%2FBrainWash_mand.jpg&h=0f796745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京對香港正式落實全面管治權，繼宣佈人大直接審議港版國安法後，教育部亦向多個省市下達指示，直接派出 「指導員」指導香港教師工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多個省市已收到《關於遴選中小學及幼兒園教師赴港澳擔任教學指導教師的通知》。<br />\n<br />\n內容是選派選派優秀大陸教師赴港澳擔任教學指導教師。根據教育部工作安排，被揀選的教師必需 「政治立場堅定」、中共黨員。赴港澳擔任為期一年的教學指導工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n赴港澳教學指導教師的主要任務<br />\n<br />\n1．承擔香港或澳門中小學語文、數學等學科的教學指導及普通話教學工作；<br />\n<br />\n2．協助香港或澳門中小學推進校本課程建設；<br />\n<br />\n3．與香港或澳門幼兒園、中小學教師合作開展教學研究；<br />\n<br />\n4．促進內港與港澳兩地中小學、幼兒園的交流與合作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n責編 胡力漢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul0525a-05252020055046.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2Fwul0525a-05252020055046.html&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY3dxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=d5306ed1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul0525a-05252020055046.html</a>"},{"pid":"ff77474820ca3c7de9bd3fa7e64cd3a3ff1bf4c9","tid":2035199,"uid":259055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}